    "IntroductionCybercriminals increasingly target businesses to steal valuable data for financial gain or other malicious purposes.",
    "As a result, businesses in the modern age are increasingly facing threats from malicious cybercriminals who are constantly looking for ways to exploit their sensitive data and information.",
    "This malicious activity can harm businesses, being incredibly costly and potentially damaging their reputations.",
    "As such, it is paramount that businesses remain vigilant and take all necessary steps to ensure their data remains secure.",
